{"tid":439473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兵敗如山倒，「日本製造」亦末路","createTime":"2017-10-18T00:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T05:01:38.000Z","uid":148531,"like":47,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"897e22f090420623b209be90ba9b9fb6050d7236","tid":439473,"uid":148531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:02:24.000Z","msg":"content farm link: <a href=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/10/18/tarnish-of-made-in-japan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2Ftarnish-of-made-in-japan%2F&d=%2BZ%2Fjv8WLWLXRcr4WRp1OX7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=441a555d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/10/18/tarnish-of-made-in-japan/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 神戶製鋼經內部調查發現，是次造假醜聞來自旗下 3 家工廠，分別是位於中國蘇州、無錫和佛山的廠房。美其名的「日本製造」，實情早有一大部分轉移到大陸設廠投產，骨子裡是「中國製造」，品質既難監管，也難以重現日本製造業既有的嚴謹規格。</span></span>"},{"pid":"10ba3ad76100b1626b25aad85246d0bb997e4dd8","tid":439473,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:04:11.000Z","msg":"咁究竟係「支那製造」出問題？定「日本製造」出問題？"},{"pid":"021da5e2a45cc15e026c79500e41ea2911b9a61a","tid":439473,"uid":72457,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:06:38.000Z","msg":"講經咩，日本公司派人去，即刻比人帶去叫雞食飯派片，唔洗一個月仲貪過大陸人"},{"pid":"599e861b64d5284de7505b6ff57868d906af20e6","tid":439473,"uid":51720,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:11:54.000Z","msg":"山高皇帝遠，要東灜廠商監管強國子公司產品品質，難度甚大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e621f389095f0d1253daddfb673e2364b163aa7","tid":439473,"uid":4574,"like":22,"dislike":5,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:16:33.000Z","msg":"完全係日本責任 監管不力<br />\n日治時期 一定鞭鳩死支那孽畜"},{"pid":"f302703d533d65519b57e14456f97463907cbce3","tid":439473,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:17:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cup.com\" data-sr-url=\"https: